name: Lucky Bird
description: Lucky Bird, a metaverse project mainly built by Singapore Weimi Foundation, focuses on infrastructure construction, economic model, and cross-game layout. In the future, Lucky Bird NFT will work with various other metaverse products to build a “public ledger” in the NFT world. With a total release of 1,000 Lucky Bird NFTs, users that own Lucky Bird NFT can become esteemed VIPs in Lucky Bird metaverse and can receive VIP-exclusive benefits, with airdropping of BIRD tokens topping the list. Future benefits and rights can be unlocked by activating the community roadmap.
